text:
Christian Serratos Has One Hot Instagram Rosita from 'The Walking Dead' has the goods. Feb 21st, 2017 Photo: Instagram/Christian Serratos 
OK, so Christian Serratos ‘ character Rosita Espinosa on The Walking Dead is annoying and will probably ruin the group’s plans to bring down The Saviors, but I think we can all forgive her because she is one hot gal. A post shared by Christian Serratos (@kishserratos) on Nov 5, 2016 at 8:33am PDT 
Serratos’ co-star on the zombie drama, Alana Masterson, is also hotter than you know , but this time around we need to focus on Serratos. The 26-year-old vegan, for all you hardcore fans out there, actually played Suzie Crabgrass in the Nickelodeon series Ned’s Declassified School Survival Guide . How that’s for a fun fact? Well, Serratos is all grownup now, and boy are we glad. 
Let’s take a look at some hot photos of the Walking Dead star thanks to her Instagram .
